1. **Čudne** su mi ove vremenske promene. (These weather changes are strange to me.)
2. Ovo je **čudna** situacija. (This is a strange situation.)
3. Ona je **čudno** gledala u mene. (She looked at me strangely.)
4. Da li je ovo **čudan** ukus? (Is this a strange taste?)
5. Njihovo ponašanje je bilo **čudno**. (Their behavior was strange.)
6. Izgovorila je **čudne** reči koje nisam razumeo. (She spoke strange words that I didn't understand.)
7. Videla sam nešto **čudno** u parku sinoć. (I saw something strange in the park last night.)
8. Ovo je **čudna** knjiga, ali mi se sviđa. (This is a strange book, but I like it.)
9. Njegov izgled je bio vrlo **čudan**. (His appearance was very strange.)
10. **Čudno** mi je što niste znali za to. (It's strange to me that you didn't know about it.)